{
  "name": "FlowCargo ROI Report Generator",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "roi-report",
        "options": {}
      },
      "name": "Webhook",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        250,
        300
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "html": "<html>\n<head>\n<style>\n  body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; }\n  .header { background: #0b0b0f; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }\n  .content { padding: 40px; }\n  .highlight { color: #7b61ff; font-weight: bold; }\n  .savings-box { background: #f0f0f5; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; margin: 20px 0; }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"header\">\n    <h1>Relatório de Economia FlowCargo</h1>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"content\">\n    <h2>Olá,</h2>\n    <p>Aqui está o detalhamento da economia projetada para sua operação:</p>\n    \n    <div class=\"savings-box\">\n      <h3>Economia Mensal Estimada: R$ {{json.body.data.savings.monthly}}</h3>\n      <h3>Economia Anual Estimada: R$ {{json.body.data.savings.yearly}}</h3>\n      <p>Horas ganhas por mês: {{json.body.data.savings.time}} horas</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <p>Baseado nos dados fornecidos:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Caminhões/dia: {{json.body.data.trucksPerDay}}</li>\n      <li>Tempo de espera atual: {{json.body.data.waitTime}} min</li>\n      <li>Custo hora: R$ {{json.body.data.hourlyCost}}</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <p>Para implementar essa economia, agende uma conversa com nossos especialistas.</p>\n  </div>\n</body>\n</html>"
      },
      "name": "Generate HTML",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.function",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        450,
        300
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "url": "https://api.pdfmonkey.io/api/v1/documents",
        "method": "POST",
        "authentication": "headerAuth",
        "headerAuth": "pdfmonkey_api_key",
        "jsonParameters": true,
        "options": {},
        "bodyParametersJson": "{\n  \"document\": {\n    \"document_template_id\": \"YOUR_TEMPLATE_ID\",\n    \"payload\": {\n      \"monthly_savings\": \"{{json.body.data.savings.monthly}}\",\n      \"yearly_savings\": \"{{json.body.data.savings.yearly}}\",\n      \"time_saved\": \"{{json.body.data.savings.time}}\"\n    },\n    \"status\": \"pending\"\n  }\n}"
      },
      "name": "Generate PDF (PDFMonkey)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        650,
        300
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "fromEmail": "noreply@flowcargo.com.br",
        "toEmail": "={{json.body.email}}",
        "subject": "Seu Relatório de ROI FlowCargo",
        "text": "Olá, segue em anexo o seu relatório de economia projetada.",
        "attachments": "data"
      },
      "name": "Send Email",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.emailSend",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        850,
        300
      ]
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "Webhook": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "Generate HTML",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    "Generate HTML": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "Generate PDF (PDFMonkey)",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    "Generate PDF (PDFMonkey)": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "Send Email",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    }
  }
}
